  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Researchers are to determine if turning on an additional unilateral DBS (deep brain
      stimulation) electrode with stimulation to the globus pallidus externa (GPe) region of the
      brain will improve insomnia (sleep).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
